    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extremely hard wood of the species Diospyros melanoxylos, native to India, having a black heartwood and a fine, even grain.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
